.TH devin-cloud-drs-build 1  "build " 
.SH NAME
devin\-cloud\-drs\-build \- Trigger an environment build and wait for it to finish
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin cloud drs build\fR [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Trigger an environment build and wait for it to finish
.PP
Starts a snapshot\-setup build of all current blueprints and polls until the build succeeds, fails, or times out.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
